<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Shlef - File Sharing for Teams</title>
    <link
      rel="icon"
      href="https://www.svgrepo.com/show/396470/file-folder.svg"
    />

    <style>
      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-gray-900"
    ><div>
      <div class="bg-indigo-600">
        <div
          class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 py-3 text-white sm:text-center md:px-8"
        >
          <p class="font-medium">
            This is a WIP! Please be patient as this website is pieced together.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <Nav client:load />
      <section class="relative">
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 py-28 md:px-8">
          <div class="space-y-5 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl text-white font-extrabold mx-auto md:text-5xl">
              Share and manage files within your organisation
              <span
                class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FBD786] to-[#f7797d]"
                >with ease...</span
              >
            </h2>
            <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-300">
              ...by using a simple, self-hostable, and secure file sharing
              platform. Say goodbye to third-party file sharing services, and
              say hello the the future. Shlef. Security, by design.
            </p>
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center gap-x-4 text-gray-400 text-sm"
            >
              <button
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-2 py-2.5 px-4 mt-3 w-full text-sm text-white font-medium bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-400 active:bg-sky-600 duration-150 rounded-lg sm:mt-0 sm:w-auto"
              >
                Download<svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  class="w-5 h-5"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M2 10a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h12.59l-2.1-1.95a.75.75 0 111.02-1.1l3.5 3.25a.75.75 0 010 1.1l-3.5 3.25a.75.75 0 11-1.02-1.1l2.1-1.95H2.75A.75.75 0 012 10z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 m-auto max-w-xs h-[357px] blur-[118px] sm:max-w-md md:max-w-lg"
          style="
            background: linear-gradient(
              106.89deg,
              rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.11) 15.73%,
              rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.41) 15.74%,
              rgba(232, 121, 249, 0.26) 56.49%,
              rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4) 115.91%
            );
          "
        >
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div id="features" class="relative py-28">
      <div
        class="relative z-10 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 text-gray-300 justify-between gap-24 lg:flex md:px-8"
      >
        <div class="max-w-xl">
          <h3 class="text-white text-3xl font-semibold sm:text-4xl">
            You're in the drivers seat.
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3">
            With Shlef, you're in control of your data. That's because for us
            privacy isn't a feature. It's a right.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-0">
          <ul class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <li class="flex gap-x-4">
              <div
                class="flex-none w-12 h-12 bg-gray-700 text-cyan-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  class="w-6 h-6"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
