              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg text-gray-100 font-semibold">Fast</h4>
                <p class="mt-3">
                  Shlef is self-hosted, and built with speed in mind. It is not
                  just fast; it is blazing fast.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-4">
              <div
                class="flex-none w-12 h-12 bg-gray-700 text-cyan-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
